[B][U]Server Stuff[/U][/B]
Add these with your other setSidebarInterface's, make sure you set them to a working ID:
[code]		setSidebarInterface(14, 17000);
		setSidebarInterface(15, 17000);
		setSidebarInterface(16, 17000);[/code]

